title: PolyBoard Pro + keygen - Crackingpatching
description:
Description: 
PolyBoard Pro-PP v6.05f PolyBoard - the program is a tool for design development and manufacturing of cabinets, is based on a powerful methodological concept. The software supports tree structures, dynamic material styles and several manufacturing methods and shows the cost of working in real time. 
The program can: 
- To count the size of the cabinet, including the slopes of the anchorbox. 
- The number of racks, shelves, doors and drawers. 
- Preparation method. 
- Cabinet material, edges and frame style of each component of the cabinet separately. 
- PolyBoard supports parametric matching links, as well as an instrument map (drills and holes) for each of the cabinet components. 
- PolyBoard PostProcessing export function is compatible with most tool machines. 

License: ShareWare - for you free of charge 
Language: English - Russian version and Russifier not available

OS: Windows
